Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.82,0:01:55.26,Sign,,0,0,100,,{\c&HA8AEAD&\bord5\blur5\3c&H4B1214&}Episode 60 \N{\fs70}Magical World {まじかるワールド}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I really die?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Light... An exit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.26,0:02:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, I feel much better now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.26,0:02:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ngh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.92,0:02:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So warm... A wonderfully pleasant place!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.07,0:03:32.30,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,300)\c&H3E341E&\3c&HB2AD81&}Edojo Honmaru
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,HONMARU!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru! Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.15,0:04:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H141C80&}Mama...{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru! Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru... Why... Why did you die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, isn't it about time \Nwe returned to the Magic Realm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go back, you might be able to see Honmaru again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.51,0:04:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, the Magic Realm exists in the world \Nwhere people go after they die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.94,0:05:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.04,0:05:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Let's hurry home to see Honmaru again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.27,0:05:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's return then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If I return, I won't be seeing everyone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta resurrect Honmaru after all! {h}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll all live together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, don't you really know some magic for resurrecting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.16,0:05:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Really don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Taru. I really don't know of any.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if Honmaru is in the Spirit World now, \Nwe can bring him to the Magic Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, if we ask our mama, she might agree to resurrect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.68,0:06:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.24,0:06:05.17,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1000)\c&HACBBBF&\3c&H6E6DBD&}Spirit World {精霊界 / seireikai}
Dialogue: 2,0:06:04.07,0:06:10.22,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,0)\c&H223E3A&\3c&HB1CCC0&}Magic Realm
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving for the Spirit World!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.80,0:06:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the spirit world? \NHow do I get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, these two worlds are governed by unbending laws. {either "there are rules you can't change" or "there's a fate that you can't return"}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, where spirit world?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.96,0:06:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The spell for going to the spirit world is the spell \Nfor returning to the Magic Realm that you already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When you use it to go home, \Nyou'll pass through the Spirit World on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! Alright, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Good day! Nice to meet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it! I'm not done talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you reach the Spirit World, you'll need to take Honmaru \Nto the Magic Realm without anyone noticing. {h}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone spots you, \Ngrab Honmaru and make a run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get caught... It's not just that Honmaru won't be resurrected. Taru, you'll be punished too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, let's go togetheru-ru-ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.94,0:07:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to know that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Only magicians who came to this world \Nupon being summoned by humans
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,can go to the Spirit World to be judged \Non whether or not they have properly trained in this world. {feels like she's making up rules on the go}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I only came to this world \Nas moral support for you. {support; prop; something upon which to rely​}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you disappear from this world, \NI'll get sucked away into the Magic Realm immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it. I gotta go alone to resurrect Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, me, Honmaru, and everyone \Nwould live together again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.59,0:08:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if Honmaru comes back to life, \Nyou won't be able to live in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Because once you return to the Magic Realm,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:09:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,until someone summons you again, \Nyou won't have any way of reappearing in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru will re-summon me \Nafter I resurrect him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,After you say the spell for returning to the Magic Realm, \Neveryone will immediately forget all about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.42,0:09:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sister, please teach me some magic \Nfor living with everyone in this world ever after!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know of any convenient magic like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama-chan, please teach me. Tama-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Taru-chan. I don't know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:10:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was thinking... \NSince Honmaru is there, in the other world,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,why don't we live together over there - \Nthe three of us and mama. Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If Honmaru resurrected,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.66,0:10:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Me forever apart from Honmaru \Nin the Magic Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.08,0:10:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If Honmaru dies, me live together with Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Me live together with Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.74,0:10:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Good day...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He died...{? TLC, assumed issho - together with mama}{10:43: I'm hearing "死ぬ"\NA loose TL would be "He's dead..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But without everyone... don't wanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:10:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, Iyona, papa, Rui,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, Jabao, Korekiyo, Matsu-san, everyone... Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's here. What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.78,0:11:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There are people!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.95,0:12:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone spots you, \Ngrab Honmaru and make a run for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.94,0:12:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.02,0:12:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:13:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do that, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Taru? \NWeren't those people calling me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, they're coming after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get caught, \NHonmaru won't be able to come back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If me ask my mom, Honmaru will come back to life, \Nand me forever apart with Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But Honmaru's mama, papa, \NIyona, Rui - everyone will be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be happy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.88,0:13:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.31,0:13:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru died. This is afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... I won't see Iyona-chan ever again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.41,0:14:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,0:14:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, we have to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.59,0:14:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, move it! \NMe bring Honmaru back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But if people chasing us catch up and catch us, \NI can't bring you back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta run! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I can fly too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In this world, you can have any power you can think of.{h}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! This feels pretty darn nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.60,0:14:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. There's the entrance to the Magic Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Taruruuto! This is my friend, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooooh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to see you've come.{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this, Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This tunnel leads to the Magic Realm. \NThose chasing us can't enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.16,0:15:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute... {no clue, tlc, was "You belong to the dead... "}{Au: 15:18: I'm hearing "本丸、待ちなさい"\NLit: "Honmaru, wait!"\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Gotta hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.86,0:15:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked! Seems like we shook them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be in the Magic Realm soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm falling! Do something, Taru! Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.09,0:16:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-chan, Honmaru-kun, \Nyou both can fly on your own, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.43,0:16:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.09,0:16:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the Magic Realm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't relax your guard just yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The spirits from earlier can still catch up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,First, let's fly towards that high mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Will see my mama again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru's mama is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My mama is the Great Magician. \NWith my mama's magic, Honmaru can be resurrected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! I'll get to see Iyona-chan in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Head towards that ball of water, surrounded by clouds from all sides. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.99,0:16:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The next would be the third island from the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The Magic Realm sure is vast.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is close to our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon enough, our home...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, he's been away from his mama \Never since I summoned him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder he misses her greatly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru's mama, then? I wonder what kind of person she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My mama very gentle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? How did you understand what I was thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In Magic Realm, what you think is what you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinda like telepathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta keep my mind away from thinking lewd things. {unsure, maybe means not himself, this koitsu perplexes me}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Me not thinking lewd things! {again, could mean "you don't think ..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a duel, Taruruuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.77,0:17:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to compete at?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Eeeeck! {assumed "hi" (fire)}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Eecking, then? {/fire}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.64,0:17:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you! How dare you fry Taru unprovoked?! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You wanna go at it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in luck today. \NI'll get two prey at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you... Why did you do this to Taru?! \NHonmaru Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.50,0:18:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He's too tough for me!{https://proverb-encyclopedia.com/hagatatanai/}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop fooling around and decide what we'll compete at!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, I'd rather not!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When he turns his back, \NI'll kick him then and there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.18,0:18:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How cowardly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! He knows immediately everything I'm thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.36,0:18:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be helped! Let's duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.34,0:18:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! What will we compete at?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Let's have a duel in rock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.05,0:18:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, we can do that, right? {/would saying so be viable?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's have a duel in rock, paper, scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.29,0:19:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky! This way, I'll at least have a chance too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot, you can easily win in rock, paper, scissors \Nif you can read the opponent's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.78,0:19:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That said, which one should I choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be rock, scissors or paper? \NIf I had to choose, rock or paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Decide already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If I throw paper, it may be a mistake... {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough! We're starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up, I've not decided yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.90,0:19:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.88,0:19:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I've not decided yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.32,0:19:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.40,0:19:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I don't understand his thoughts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.99,0:19:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Seems like I won.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.78,0:19:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit, I lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as easy as that! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll be taking that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Scroll! {assumed some counter word but no clue why he'd use that, just "ryuu" in kana in manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Trunsform!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Give Taru back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.06,0:20:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, you're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, after defeating you, \NI've collected ten stamps already!{/stars}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.28,0:20:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You beat me at rock, paper, scissors, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.41,0:20:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Honmaru, you can use this. \NIt's still brand new. {/not used at all}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.81,0:20:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, you need to produce a spell of youru-ru-ru own!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Spell of my own?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.85,0:20:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-ru-ru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.37,0:20:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When you win a duel in Magic Realm, \Nyou make a stamp of your opponent and press it on a scroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:21:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you collect a lot of stamps, you can return the scroll \Nand exchange them for magical items.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone here duels a lot. \NThis is also magical training.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm. Taru-chan, if you don't hurry, \Nthe spirits will find and catch you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.27,0:21:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I completely forgot! Let's hurry, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.72,0:21:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.69,0:21:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Our home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.25,0:21:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Made! We made! We made it, made it, made it, made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.78,0:21:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Brought Honmaru to our home!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.81,0:22:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you call home?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.06,0:22:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.86,0:22:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.01,0:22:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.25,0:22:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.74,0:22:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, I'm coming home!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.96,0:22:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Taru's mama can't bring me back to life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.48,0:22:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, what do I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.06,0:22:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry, Honmaru. The Colored Sky Hermit \Non Ice Spirit Mountain can still help you. {氷霊山の色空仙人, no clue what's this ninai}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.33,0:22:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! Soon enough, dad, mom, Iyona-chan, \NIyona-chan, Iyona-chan, Iyona-chan, just you wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.63,0:23:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, do your best!
